{"tid":809049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土壤液化　人車深陷泥濘","createTime":"2018-09-06T23:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T00:54:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eccc850ab1db8b7832779b5bd6ec2df25ddc54cd","tid":809049,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:58:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180907/20494045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20494045&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KC9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=f8dd73e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F20494045&h=2dabc789\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180907/20494045</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月07日 <br />\n<br />\n土壤液化　人車深陷泥濘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180907/large/1536253807_0923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536253807_0923.jpg&h=e2a3b6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【旭川】旭川機場在震後照明系統失靈，旅客需用電筒輔助尋找行李。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n今次北海道地震，札幌市內和近海的厚真町都出現「土壤液化」，樹木如水瀉，人車深陷泥砂中。專家指出，土壤液化要具備三個元素，分別是鬆軟的砂層、高地下水位及強烈的地震。<br />\n<br />\n早前颱風「飛燕」帶來暴雨，浸鬆泥土，已促成前兩個條件；強震一來，即破壞地層間水和泥沙的平衡，土壤水份被擠壓到表面，造成泥沙噴出地面、地層下陷的駭人景象。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180907/large/a02a02a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180907%2Flarge%2Fa02a02a.gif&h=95c11824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東京大地震研究所教授加藤愛太郎說，「液化」多發生在地底火山灰積聚或含砂量高的區域；另外，填海土地亦容易在地震時出現土壤液化，1995年阪神大地震，神戶人工島就出現液化現象。<br />\n<br />\n日本山泥傾瀉學會會長、地貌學教授八木浩司則補充，除了以上因素，在厚真町的震源就在腳下，造成的破壞更大；他警告山林隨時再度崩塌，沿河建築物要特別注意。<br />\n<br />\n時事通訊社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港團370人滯留　部份繼續行程<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n日本今年天災連連<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直下型淺層地震　能量如5.6顆原子彈<br />\n<br />\n強烈餘震勢來襲　港人：驚返唔到嚟<br />\n<br />\n港人滯留札幌憂「糧盡」直擊市面車站斷電<br />\n<br />\n港團370人滯留　部份繼續行程<br />\n<br />\n日本今年天災連連<br />\n<br />\n6.7級地震　11死32失蹤北海道山崩地裂"},{"pid":"4fa04f977b57d326cbfc179effd67b99af1ebcb5","tid":809049,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd177408392c3b7f0fec747d9c3f37fbb387b26c","tid":809049,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645ae0a324b941804feaaf3679e91bceebdaf1aa","tid":809049,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"好似第一次聽呢個詞語"},{"pid":"f174581daeaecb4eaa01765d5194aec47ca59bac","tid":809049,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"港豬奧人工島會唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2ad0257be0a80c19d4a28a72a48b9432cfb9f6","tid":809049,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645ae0a324b941804feaaf3679e91bceebdaf1aa","tid":809049,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"好似第一次聽呢個詞語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:54:24.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲都有"}]}